snippet.title: Multifemale | I kneel before no one.
snippet.description:
“So you wanna play with magic?”

Watch in 1080p and with headphones.

NOTE: I do not support Amber Heard. I do not condone abuse. I simply liked her character in Aquaman and thought she fit the criteria for the video. I apologize. I will keep the viewers preference in mind for future videos.

___________

Fandom(s): WandaVision, The New Mutants, Huntsman: Winter’s War, Maleficent, Dark Phoenix, Snow White and the Huntsman, The Chilling Adventures of Sabrina, Aquaman, The Gifted, Captain Marvel, Wonder Woman, Game of Thrones, X-men: Apocalypse
Song: Dark Horse | Katy Perry (no rap version which can be found here: https://youtu.be/v4DP5jNfgxw)

I do not anything but the editing in this video.

#ViddingIsArt #Multifemale
